<span class="c"># For Linux, Option: 2, using normal/ Desktop interface mode</span>
<span class="gp">$ </span>&lt;ZAP_HOME&gt;./zap.sh 

<span class="c"># For Windows, Run the exe file or zap.bat script to start the ZAP</span>
</code></pre><pre class="highlight java tab-java"><code><span class="c1">// For Linux, Option: 1, using "headless/daemon" mode</span>
